Major modifications in this fork include:
  - Rebranding from the upstream desktop assistant lineage to OpenScience.
  - Science Mode planning and research-project workflow documentation.
  - Medical Evidence Mode, source-labeled report surfaces, and evidence
    workflow integrations.
  - Scientific artifact preview concepts for figures, tables, reports,
    notebooks, manuscripts, code, logs, review status, and source trails.
  - New README images, localized README files, generated brand assets,
    and OpenScience-specific product documentation.
  - Additional local MCP/tooling plans and research workflow integrations.

